@10016   = ~Scimitar of the Poisoned Fang~
@10017   = ~The scimitar, or "shamshir" as it was originally called, has a single-edged blade with a significant curve, and is tapered to an elongated, sharp point.~
@10018   = ~It is said that this weapon was created by Revialis the Serpent out of reverence to Talona, and that his devotion to the Lady of Poison can still be seen in its deep red glow. It is uncertain how this scimitar made its way from Memnon, the place of its forging, into the hands of a half-orc sailor, but now that it is found, it will no doubt play some part in the legends that are even now unfolding.


