@10026   = ~Assassin's Helper~
@10027   = ~In Skullport, the city-beneath-a-city that lies a mile below Waterdeep, life is cheap, and it is most certainly for sale. This slender, non-descript dagger has proven a useful tool in the negotiations. Looking at it, in fact, there is hardly anthing that would suggest the enchantments that make it the lethal weapon that it is. Merely weilding it enhances stealth, and magics placed upon the blade ensure that it strikes swift... and deep.


