@10028   = ~Quicksilver~
@10029   = ~This shiny silver dagger was found sticking out of a hay bale in a tiny fishing village on the northern Sword Coast. Retrieving it was nothing akin to pulling a sword from a stone, but it is a prize, nonetheless. It is hard to tell if the wielder of this blade is moving faster than anybody else, or if everyone else is just moving slower, but one thing is true. The wielder cannot be slowed or stunned. Additionally, there is a chance that anyone struck by this dagger will be slowed. 


