@10041   = ~Cloak of Insulation +2~
@10042   = ~The cloak can be made in every possible shape with just about every type of fabric. The most common forms are a circular piece of fabric with a hole in the center for the head, and fabric draped from neck, connected by a chain, brooch, cord, or pins.~
@10043   = ~Cloak of Insulation +2: 'Firian's Embrace' 

When Firian Killeraheal wrapped his beloved Amanis in this cloak for her journey from Myth Drannor to Suldanessellar, he wished to protect her from every peril she might encounter along the way. She arrived in safety, but he perished in a shipwreck on the Sea of Fallen Stars. Grieving, Amanis departed for Arvandor, leaving behind this cloak in memory of her love.


